commentTextItems.html: on the legs and flicked through mid wicket for a boundary and that's the match for West Indies

commentPostTextItems.html: Captain Bravo came out and struck a few lusty blows for his team to seal the match.West Indies win the match by 6 wickets without breaking a sweat. Zimbabwe have tapered away after a great start to the series and have quite an effort on their hands to win the series, as they have to win both the matches.
Join us for our coverage of the next match on friday at Bulawayo.

commentTextItems.html: flicks it over square leg for a boundary
slower ball on the legs, flicked to long leg for a single
turned of his hips to mid wicket
off the pads behind square for a  leg bye
wide outside off and called a wide
on the legs and flicked to fine leg for a couple
